timeline.bodyText:
Surely an extra overload method in Perspective.java
public static Polygon getCanvasTileAreaPoly(
		@Nonnull Client client,
		@Nonnull LocalPoint localLocation,
		int size)
	{
    getCanvasTileAreaPoly(client, localLocation, size, 0);
}

Is better than adding a zero on every usage?

